FIRST NAT. BANK OF SYRACUSE, Respondent, v. WILCOX, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by the First National Bank of Syracuse against Dwight Wilcox, impleaded, etc.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Order reversed, with $10 costs and disbursements, and motion denied, with $10 costs.
